mco.account.privacy.info: Ɣer ugar ɣef Mojang d tsertiyin n tbaḍnit
mco.account.privacyinfo:
Mojang tteẓẓu kra n yikalaten i tallelt n uḥuddu n yigruden d tbaḍnit-nsen, rnu-as amtawi akked Arra n uḥuddu n tbaḍnit n tuqqna n yigruden (COPPA) akked Uslagan n uḥuddu n yisefka amatu (GDPR). 

Ad tesriḍ ad tesɛuḍ urag n yimawlan uqbel ad ak-nanef ad tadfeḍ amiḍan Realms.

Ma yella tesɛiḍ amiḍan Minecraft aqbur (ad tkecmeḍ s yisem useqdac), ad tesriḍ ad terreḍ amiḍan-a ɣer yiwen umiḍan Mojang i wakken ad tadfeḍ Realms.
